        "content": "## Tailwind – List Boards helper (run once)\n\nPulls every Pinterest board name + ID from Tailwind into the **Tailwind Boards** tab, so you can copy the IDs into **Board Map**.\n\n**Setup:** create a tab named **Tailwind Boards** with headers: Pinterest Account | Board Name | Board ID. Set the Google Sheets + Tailwind (Bearer) credentials. Then click Execute.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "sticky",
      "name": "README",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -360,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "n-trig",
      "name": "Run Once",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
